org.jdrupes.httpcodec.fields

Class HttpStringListField

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jdrupes.httpcodec.fields.HttpField<java.util.List<T>>
      • org.jdrupes.httpcodec.fields.HttpListField<java.lang.String>
        • org.jdrupes.httpcodec.fields.HttpStringListField
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.String>, java.util.Collection<java.lang.String>, java.util.List<java.lang.String>

    public class HttpStringListField
extends HttpListField<java.lang.String>
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    An HTTP field value that consists of a comma separated list of strings. The class provides a "list of strings" view of the values.
    Author:
    Michael N. Lipp
